The paper focuses on IoT security and privacy, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI). The authors also discuss software design and big data analytics in the cloud, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions modeling and simulations, which can be categorized under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
